<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2c3e50;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Hotel Amin International</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Reservation Confirmed!</h2>
      <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for booking with Hotel Amin International! We're excited to welcome you. Below are the details of your reservation:</p>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Reservation ID</th>
          <td>{{booking_id}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Check-in Date</th>
          <td>{{checkin_date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Check-out Date</th>
          <td>{{checkout_date}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Room Numbers</th>
          <td>{{room_num}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Guests</th>
          <td>{{number_of_guests}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Total Price</th>
          <td>{{total_price}} Tk</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>If you need to modify or cancel your reservation, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@hotelamininternational.com">info@hotelamininternational.com</a> or call +1-555-123-4567.</p>
      
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Hotel Amin International | 1234 Serenity Lane, Paradise City<br>
      +1-555-123-4567 | <a href="mailto:info@hotelamininternational.com.com">info@hotelamininternational.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>